txt.en: 'Meow! Back so soon? Well I can complete Book II of the Epic quest series now for you, if you'd like. Just speak to me again.
'Alright, when you complete this quest you'll be flagged as having completed Book II of the Epic. Have fun!'
Level Up: Volume II: Book II
Completion of this quest will flag your character has having completed all the quests in Book II of the Epic quest series for Volume II.
